# Prisma & Database Rules

- Schema: `client/prisma/schema.prisma`
- After every schema change: `npx prisma generate --schema=client/prisma/schema.prisma` then `npx prisma db push --schema=client/prisma/schema.prisma`
- **Never** use `prisma migrate` — intentional for air-gapped deployment
- Column renames = drop+add in DB; rename field and update all references in the **same PR**
- No rollback path — destructive `db push` changes lose data; coordinate with team
- Restart backend after `db push`
- DB: PostgreSQL in `lms-qaf-app-db` (`military_lms` / `military_lms123` @ localhost:5432)
